ygData.messageBody:
From an online music dictionary
(http://www.creativemusic.com/features/dictionary.html(

Cantata: "Sung". A multi-movement vocal work for concert or church
performance by a choir, sometimes soloists, and an instrumental ensemble.


- FB

>Does anyone know or has anyone heard if they are going to fix the name of

that typo, but now it's going to drive me crazy. Thanks a lot! :-p

I vote for listening to Santana of Soothing at the cantina con mucho
tequila! Vamanos Muchachos!

---Windleaf
